#!CDarkGreen #!N  #!Rall12 View Control #!N #!EC The  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   
View Control #!EF dialog box allows you to control (among other 
aspects of an object) the following: #!N #!I0 #!N  #!F-adobe-times-medium-r-normal--18*   #!N 
#!N #!I30 #!N o Viewing direction #!N #!I30 #!N o Rotation 
#!N #!I30 #!N o Field of view (zooming and panning). #!N 
#!I0 #!N #!EF #!N #!N #!N To open this dialog box, 
select  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   View Control... #!EF in the  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   Options #!EF pull-down 
menu in the Image window. #!N #!N #!N  #!F-adobe-times-medium-i-normal--18*   Next Topic 
